### 9. Proven Anthropic L3 idioms to reuse (LogScale)
- Distinct total: `request_id = * | groupBy([request_id]) | count()`
- Failure flag: `is_fail := if(condition=regex(field=message, "origin_status_code=[45]\d{2}"), then=1, else=0)`
- Per-request rollup: `groupBy([request_id], function=max(is_fail, as=req_failed))`
- Single KPI: `key := "all" | groupBy([key], function=[...])`
- Latency: `"execution statistics:" | regex(field=message, "'<provider>':\s*(?<latency>\d+\.\d+)") | percentile(field=latency, percentiles=[95])`
- Generalized model regex (Vertex): `models/(?<model>[^/@:"]+)`

